                      div.small Not deep expertise, but understanding to use AI tools effectively
                  li.list-group-item.d-flex.align-items-start
                    .ms-2.me-auto
                      .fw-bold Embrace Rapid Iteration
                      div.small Using AI to accelerate learning and development cycles

              .col-lg-6
                h4.mb-3
                  i.bi.bi-building.me-2
                  | For Organizations:
                ul.list-group.list-group-flush
