                    i.bi.bi-diagram-3.text-info.me-3.mt-1
                    div
                      strong Redesign workflows to leverage AI
                      div.text-muted.small Integrate amplifying tools throughout operations
                  li.list-group-item.d-flex.align-items-start.border-0.ps-0
                    i.bi.bi-people.text-warning.me-3.mt-1
                    div
                      strong Rethink credentialing and hiring
                      div.text-muted.small Prioritize demonstrated agency over formal qualifications

          // Conclusion Section
          section.mb-5
            .card.bg-dark.text-white
              .card-body.py-5
                h2.h3.mb-4.text-center.text-white
                  i.bi.bi-sunrise.text-warning.me-2
                  | Conclusion: The Age of the Self-Starter

                p.lead.text-center.mb-4.text-white
                  | We stand at the beginning of a new era where the primary limitation on what an individual can
                  | accomplish isn't knowledge, credentials, or resources, but rather the willingness to take initiative.

                blockquote.blockquote.text-center.mb-4
